name: A Kick of Fire
description:
In Indonesia’s wayang story, Hanuman was captured and burned alive. But he manage to escape and set the kingdom of Alengka on fire. This photo was taken from the Kecak Dance. The performer of Hanuman is dancing with his barefoot while stepping and kicking the fire in this scene.
----------
Size: 4940 x 3403

Res: 240px/inch

Canon 60D, 50mm, f/2, 1/500, ISO 800

loc: Bali
